    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FLORIDA IS JUST A\nPEOPLE EXPRESS\nPRICE AWAY.\nSYSTEM FLIGHT SCHEDULE EFFECTIVE FEB 11 THRU APRIL 26\nFT. LAUDERDALE• ORLANDO • MIAMI\nSARASOTA/BRADENTON • FT. MYERS\nST. PETERSBURG/TAMPA • JACKSONVILLE\nWEST PALM BEACH • MELBOURNE",
      "ANNOUNCING SAVINGS\nAS BIG AS AMERICA ITSELE\nSASKATOONa\nREGINA/MOOSE JAWO\n•WINNIPEG\nNON STOP TO BRUSSELS\nVANCOUVER\nKALISPELLO\nSEATTLE\n@SPOKANE\nGREAT FALLS\n\"MISSOULA\nBOZEMAN\n•DILLINGS\n\"EUGEME\n9WEST YELLOWSTONE,\nQUACKSUN\nCASPERO\nFRONTIER\n•FARGO\nBISMARCK\nMONTREAL\nRAPID CITY\n•SIOUX FALLS\n•MINNEAPOLIS\n?BURLINGTUNE\n§PORTLAND\nBUFFALOE\nOSTRACUSE\nBOSTON\nSALT LAKE CITY-\n• КЕТАНОЕ\nCEDAR RAPIDSO\nOOMAHA DES MOIMES CHICAGO CLEVELANDO\nOLINCULN\nNEW YORK/NEWARK\nPEOPLE EXPRESS\nSACRAMENTO\nGARLANDO\nSAN FRANCISCO STOCKTON,\nGRAND JUNCTION\nWASHINGTON SO C\nÓLAS VEGAS\n•ALBUQUERQUE\nST. LOUIS\nWICHITA SPRINGFIELD\nOTULSÁ\n•OKLAHOMA CITY\nNASHVILLE\n- GREENSBORO\nCHARLOTTE\nLOS ANGELESO\nORANGE\nPHOEMIX\nCOLUMBIA\nDALLAS\nFT. WORTH\nOTUCSON\n•EL PASO\nMIDLAND/\nODESSA\nBIRMINGHAMO\n•ATLANTA\nHOUSTON®\nNEWUNLEANDO\nJACKSONVILLEd\nORLANDO o\nST. PETERSB\n150\nO MELBOURNE\nSARASOTA/BRADENTONO\n© WEST PALM BEACH\nFT. MYERSO\nOFT. LAUDERDALE\nMIAMTO\nLONDON\nGATWICK O\nBRUSSELS\nPeople Express is joining with Frontier Airlines to fly you anywhere\non the map at a remarkable price. And, as always, we give you these\nlow prices every seat, every flight, every day.\nPeople Express has always offered you unrestricted savings. Now,\nteamed with Frontier, we offer unrestricted cities."
